snippet.title: Uncanny Cat golf (Longplay)
snippet.description:
Game: https://slappyhappy2000.itch.io/uncanny-cat-golf
Author: SHK2 (SlappyHappy2000) @SlappyHappy2000 

Why do I keep playing random shit I found on internet man.
This game popped up on my Twitter timeline and then someone linked the game, I thought it was just a dumb video for shits n giggles and no, it's a game, and it's golf, and it has a screamer around the minute 30:43, marking it down so YOU can skip it because I didn't edited the video, I'm uploading this as it is, still fuck you for putting a screamer.
This is a meme game (and also golf, which is kinda the same thing) where you control the canny cat (Idk if that is the name for the cat I know almost nothing about these) and have to put it in the hole, like, golf, all this while dodging the uncanny cat and the different obstacles the game throws at you, from smiley faces, skulls, cars, switches, all that, it's fucking golf at the end of the day. 
Every level has a different level design and hazard to overcome across  and a half world, the game ends at world 4-5 since this is pretty much a demo.
And just now noticed I forgot to check the "Show mouse" option on my recorder program, ffs

I liked this even with the funny Screamer, my only suggestions are, maybe controller support and a resolution setting, because I couldn't resize the window.

And that's it, If you want to kill a few neurons and time, try this thing, it's 1 hour long at max.
